This demo provides information concerning the setup of a basic, non-modular
web application, cli and testing environments using the parables library.

The primary files of interest are:

/path/to/parables-demo/application/config/application.ini
/path/to/parables-demo/scripts/doctrine.sh
/path/to/parables-demo/tests/index.php
/path/to/parables-demo/tests/phpunit.xml

See http://github.com/mlurz71/parables for more information.

